\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6383391\charrsid7502071 taught}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7996314\charrsid7502071  to say prayers at night?
