No, no. Oh no, he always kept clear of that. Oh yes, I never knew father to get anywhere where there was fighting. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8985554 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7996314\charrsid7502071 Do you know why he held Liberal views?
