 - yes, always seemed more friendly to be called George. Of course Miss Watts and Miss Fister, they always called me Richer. Always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8985554 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7996314\charrsid7502071 What did Sir John call the coachman?
