Oh yes, she used to make a lot of puddings. And of course we had plenty of vegetable. Oh yes. Oh plenty of vegetable.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8985554 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7996314\charrsid7502071 You had a garden?
