railway ticket for a week or a fortnight, whatever holiday we got, we used to hire a beach hut. The two girls used to go to their aunties at Clacton, sleep there, we used to come home of the nights, then go down again early in the morning. As we went down
 we used to get enough food to take down to the hut for the day.
